The average mobile data speed
in Vietnam, India, Argentina,

00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:17.030
Brazil is below 4
megabytes per second.

00:16:17.030 --> 00:16:20.120
And the relative cost of
data in emerging market

00:16:20.120 --> 00:16:23.000
is about 10 times higher
compared to that in the UK.

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:27.200
So think about fast apps that
are reliable and lightweight

00:16:27.200 --> 00:16:30.530
in order to best cater for the
next billion users and leverage

00:16:30.530 --> 00:16:32.320
that growth going forward.

