who connect to the internet

00:18:23.410 --> 00:18:24.979
actually experience
that connection

00:18:24.979 --> 00:18:26.020
via their mobile devices.

00:18:26.020 --> 00:18:29.860
So tablets, computers
are not as prevalent

00:18:29.860 --> 00:18:33.040
as mobile devices are.

00:18:33.040 --> 00:18:34.540
So in terms of
Nigeria-- and Nigeria

00:18:34.540 --> 00:18:36.300
is a very, very large market.

00:18:36.300 --> 00:18:40.360
We're just under 200 million
people in terms of population.

00:18:40.360 --> 00:18:43.757
