economy in the continent.

00:18:43.757 --> 00:18:45.340
But what is really,
really interesting

00:18:45.340 --> 00:18:47.995
is that we have a lot of
mobile connectivity, at least

00:18:47.995 --> 00:18:49.120
compared to everybody else.

00:18:49.120 --> 00:18:50.914
So we're just under
100 million people

00:18:50.914 --> 00:18:52.080
who connect to the internet.

00:18:52.080 --> 00:18:55.030
Mostly, via mobile devices.

00:18:55.030 --> 00:18:57.940
In terms of people who actually
have access to mobile phones,

00:18:57.940 --> 00:19:00.430
or the number of like
mobile lines that we have in

00:19:00.430 --> 00:19:03.340
the country is
